==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kinit
<hw>Kin"it</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>kinei^n</grk>
to move.]</ety> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>A unit of force equal to the
force which, acting for one second, will give a pound a velocity of one
foot per second; -- proposed by <person>J. D. Everett</person>, an
English physicist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

